go install github.com/f8f8f8ff/discord/discordsend@latest

Usage of discordsend:
  -content string
    	REQUIRED. also read from stdin
  -ping
    	ping @everyone
  -status string
    	one of info, warning, error. [DISCORD_STATUS]
  -time
    	include timestamp at start of message (default true)
  -title string
    	optional title for message. [DISCORD_TITLE]
  -url string
    	REQUIRED: discord webhook url [DISCORD_HOOK_URL]
  -username string
    	override username. [DISCORD_USERNAME]
